name: DAOhaus
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
This HAUS doesn't build itself
It takes a community, and HausDAO is the community of contributors working together directly to design, build, and communicate the actual product.
